title: Jidenna Announces Debut Album The Chief , Shares New Song “The Let Out” Ft. Quavo: Listen
text:
Jidenna Announces Debut Album The Chief , Shares New Song “The Let Out” Ft. Quavo: Listen The new album is out later this month Jidenna Photo by Brian Stukes/WireImage 
Jidenna has officially announced his debut studio album. It’s called The Chief , and it’s out February 17 via Wondaland Records / Epic . The “Classic Man” has also shared a new song from the full-length—listen to “The Let Out” below. It features Migos ’ Quavo. Check out a teaser video for The Chief below as well, soundtracked by Jidenna’s song “Long Live the Chief.” Artists In This Story
